hadiths[182]{hadithnumber,text}:
6412,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa  ''do ne'matein aisi hain ke aksar log unki qadr nahi kartey, sihat aur faraaghat.'' Abbas Anbari ne bayan kya ke ham se Safwan bin Esa ne bayan kya, unse Abdullah-bin-Ubai Hind ne, unse unke walid ne ke maine Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi hadis ki tarah ."
6413,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (اللهم لا عيش إلا عيش الآخره ، Mina padhi. فأصلح الأنصار والمهاجره) ''aey Allah ! aakhirat ki zindagi ke siwa aur koi zindagi nahi. isliiye to Ansar w muhajireen mein salaah ko baqi rakh.''
6414,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par maujood they, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi khandaq khodtey jatey they aur ham mitti ko uthatey jatey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey qareeb se guzartey huey farmaatey                         (اللهم لا عيش إلا عيش الآخره ، Mina فاغفر للأنصار والمهاجره) ''aey Allah ! zindagi to bas aakhirat hi ki zindagi hai, isliiye tu ansaar w muhajireen ki maghfirat kar.'' us riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ki hai."
6415,maine aapko ye farmatey huey suna ke jannat mein aik kode jitni jagah duniya aur is mein jo kuchh hai sabse behtar hai aur Allah ke rastey mein subah ko ya Sham ko thoda sa chalnaa bhi duniya aur jo kuch usmein hai se behtar hai.
6416,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mera shana pakad kar farmaya ''duniyaa mein is tarah ho ja jaisey to musaafir ya rasta chalney wala ho.''  Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they Sham ho jaey to subah ke muntazir na raho aur subah ke waqt Sham (Syria) ke muntazir na raho, apni seihat ko marz se pahley ghaneemat jano aur zindagi ko maut se pahley ."
6417,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chaukhtaa khat kheenchaa . phir iske darmyan aik khat kheenchaa jo chaukhtey ke darmyan mein tha. iske baad darmyan waley khat ke us hissey mein jo chaukhtey ke darmyan mein tha chhotey chhotey bahut se khutoot kheenchey aur phir farmaya ke ye insan hai aur ye uski maut hai jo usey gherey huey hai aur ye jo (beech ka ( khat bahar nikla hua hai wo uski ummeed hai aur chhotey chhotey khutoot uski duniyawi mushkilaat hain. isliiye insan jab aik (mushkil) se bach kar nikalta hai to dusri mein phans jata hai aur dusri se nikalta hai to teesri mein phans jata hai.
6418,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand khutoot kheenchey aur farmaya ke ye ummeed hai aur ye maut hai, insan usi haalat (ummeed tak pahunchne ki) mein rehta hai ke qareeb wala khat (maut) us tak pahunch jata hai."
6419,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ne us aadmi ke uzr ke silsiley mein hujjat tamam kar di jiski maut ko dair huii  yahan tak ke wo saa'tth (60) saal ki umr ko pahunch gaya. ''us riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) abu-Hazim aur ibne-ajlaan ne Maqbari se ki.
6420,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''boodhey insan ka dil do chizon ke barey mein hamesha jawan rehtaa hai, duniya ki mohabbat aur zindagi ki lambi ummeed.'' Leis ne bayan kya ke mujh se Yunus ne bayan kya aur Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se bayan kya ke mujhey Saeed aur abu-Salma ne khabar di."
6421,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' insan ki umr badhtii jati hai aur uske sath do cheezein uske andar badhtii jati hain. maal ki mohabbat aur umr ki daraazii.'' uski riwayat Shoba ne Qatada se ki hai.
6422,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ye baat khub mere zahan mein mehfooz hai. unhein yad hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke aik dol mein se pani lekar mujh par kulli kar di thi.
6423,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey aur farmaya ''koii banda jab qiyamat ke din us haalat mein pesh hoga ke usne kalima ( لا إله إلا الله (ka iqrar kya hoga aur is se uska maqsad Allah ki khushnoodii hasil karna hogi to Allah Taala dozakh ki aag ko is par haram kar dega.''
6424,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala farmata hai ke mere us momin bandey ka jis ki, mein koi azeez cheez duniya se utha loon aur wo is par sawab ki niyat se sabr kar ley , to uska badla mere yahan jannat ke siwa aur kuchh nahi. ''"
6425,"Amr-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) jo bani Aamir bin Adi ke dost they aur badr ki ladai main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, unhon-ne unhein khabar di ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ko Bahrain wahan ka jiziya laney ke liye bhejaa, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bahrain walon se suleh kar li thi aur un par Alaa-bin-Al-Hizramii (الحضرمی) ko ameer muqarrar kya tha. jab abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) Bahrain se jiziya ka maal lekar aaey to Ansar ne unke aaney ke mutaalliq suna aur subah ki Namaz Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padhi aur jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein dekh kar muskuraaey aur farmaya mera khayal hai ke abu-Ubaida ke aaney ke mutaalliq tum ne sun liya hai aur ye bhi ke wo kuchh lekar aaey hain? Ansar ne arz kya : ji haan , ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tumhen khushkhabri ho tum uski ummeed rakho jo tumhen khush kar degi , Allah ki qism ! ghariibii w mohtaajii wo cheez nahi hai jis se main tumharey mutaalliq darta hun balke main to us se darta hun ke duniya tum par bhi isi tarah kushaada kar di jaeygi, jis tarah un logon par kar di gaee thi jo tum se pahley they aur tum bhi uske liye aik doosrey se aagey badhney ki isi tarah koshish karogey jis tarah wo kartey they aur tumhen bhi isi tarah ghaafil kar degi jis tarah unko ghaafil kya tha."
6426,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur jange-Uhud ke shaheedon ke liye is tarah Namaz padhi jis tarah murda par Namaz padhi jati hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mimber par tashrif laey aur farmaya aakhirat mein main tum se aagey jaaunga aur main tum par gawah hunga , Allah ki qism main apne hauz ko us waqt bhi dekh raha hun aur mujhey zameen ke khazaanon ki kunjiyaan di gaee hain ya (farmaayaa ke) zameen ki kunjiyaan di gaee hain aur Allah ki qism ! main tumharey mutaalliq us se nahi darta ke tum mere baad shirk karogey balke mujhey tumharey mutaalliq ye khof hai ke tum duniya ke liye aik doosrey se aagey badhney ki koshish karne lago gey ."
6427,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumharey mutaalliq sabse zyada us se khof khata hon ke jab Allah Taala zameen ki barkatein tumharey liye nikal dega. puchha gaya zameen ki barkatein kya hain? farmaya ke duniya ki chamak damak , is par aik sahabi ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha kya bhalai se burai paida ho sakti hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par khamosh ho gaey aur ham ne khayal kya ke shayad aap par wahi nazil ho rahi hai. iske baad apni peshani ko saaf karne lagey aur malum farmaya, poochhney waley kahan hain? poochhney waley ne kaha ke hazir hun. Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jab us sawal ka hal hamarey samney aa gaya to ham ne un sahib ki tareef ki. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bhalai se to sirf bhalai hi paida hoti hai lekin ye maal sar-sabz aur khushgawaar (ghaas ki tarah) hai aur jo cheez bhi Rabe ke mausam mein ugtii hain wo laalech ke sath khaney walon ko halaak kar deti hain ya halaakat ke qareeb pahuncha deti hain. siwaey us janwar ke jo pet bhar ke khaaey ke jab us ne kha liya aur uski donon kokh bhar gain to usne suraj ki taraf munh karke jugaalii kar li aur phir pakhana peshab kar diya aur uske baad phir lot ke kha liya aur ye maal bhi bahut meethaa hai jisne usey haq ke sath liya aur haq mein kharch kya to wo behtreen zariia' hai aur jisne usey naajaaiz tareeqe se hasil kya to wo us shakhs jaisa hai jo khata hai lekin ranjeedaa nahi hota."
6428,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein sabse behtar mera zamana hai, phir un logon ka zamana hai jo uske baad hongey. '' Imran ne bayan kya ke mujhey nahi malum Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat ko do martaba dohraya ya teen martaba . phir iske baad wo log hongey ke wo gawahi dengey lekin unki gawahi qabool nahi ki jaeygi, wo khayanat karengey aur un par se bharosaa jata rahega. wo nazar maanein gey lekin poori nahi karengey aur unmein mutaapaa phail jaeyga"
6429,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sabse behtar mera zamana hai, iske baad un logon ka jo iske baad hongey phir jo unke baad hongey aur uske baad aisey log paida hongey jo qism se pehley gawahi dengey kabhi gawahi se pehley qism khaaengey.''"
6430,"maine Khubbaab-bin-Arat (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, us din unke pet mein saat (7) dagh lagaey gaey they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne agar hamein maut ki dua karne se mana na kya hota to main apni maut ki dua karta. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba guzar gaey aur duniya ne unke (aa'maal khair mein se) kuchh nahi ghataayaa aur ham ne duniya se itna kuchh hasil kya ke mitti ke siwa uski koi jagah nahi."
6431,"main Khubbaab-bin-Arat (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, wo apne makan ki diwar banwaa rahe they, unhon-ne kaha ke hamarey sathi jo guzar gaey duniya ne unke nek aamaal mein se kuchh kami nahi ki lekin unke baad ham ko itna paisaa (پیسہ) mila ke ham usko kahan kharch karein bas is mitti aur pani yani Imaarat mein ham ko usey kharch ka mauqa mila hai."
6432,ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hijrat ki thi aur iska qissa bayan kya.
6433,"main Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye wuzu ka pani lekar aaya wo chabootrey par baithey huey they, phir unhon-ne achi tarah wuzu kya. iske baad kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi jagah wuzu kartey huey dekha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne achi tarah wuzu kya, phir farmaya ke jisne is tarah wuzu kya aur phir masjid mein aa kar do rakaat Namaz padhi to uske pichhley gunah maaf ho jatey hain. bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par ye bhi farmaya ke is par maghroor (مغرور) na ho jao."
6434,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''neik log ek baad doosrey guzar jaeinge iske baad jau ke bhoosey ya khajoor ke kachrey ki tarah kuchh log duniya mein reh jaeinge jinki Allah paak ko kuchh zara bhi parwaa na hogi. '' imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha (حفالة) aur (حثالة‏ ( donon ke aik mana hain.
6435,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''diinaar w dirham ke bandey , umda reshamii chaadaron ke bandey , siyah kamlii ke bandey , tabah ho gaey ke agar unhein diya jaey to wo khush ho jatey hain aur agar na diya jaey to naraz rahtey hain.''"
6436,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar insan ke paas maal ki do wadiyan hon to teesri ka khaahishmand hoga aur insan ka pait mitti ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi bhar sakti aur Allah us shakhs ki tauba qabool karta hai jo (dil se) sachchii tauba karta hai.''"
6437,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar insan ke paas maal ( bhaid-bakrii ( ki poori wadi ho to wo chaahega ke usey waisii hi aik aur mil jaey aur insan ki aankh mitti ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi bhar sakti aur jo Allah se tauba karta hai, wo uski tauba qabool karta hai'' Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujhey malum nahi ye Quran mein se hai ya nahi. bayan kya ke maine ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye member par kehtey suna tha."
6438,maine Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko Makka Mukarrama mein member par ye kehtey suna. unhon-ne apne khutbe mein kaha ke aey logo ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke agar insan ko aik wadi sona bhar ke de diya jaey to wo dusri ka khaahishmand rahega agar dusri de di jaey to teesri ka khaahishmand rahega aur insan ka pet mitti ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi bhar sakti aur Allah paak uski tauba qabool karta hai jo tauba kare.
6439,aur unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar insan ke paas soney ki aik wadi ho to wo chaahega ke 2 ho jayen aur iska munh qabr ki mitti ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi bhar sakti aur Allah uski tauba qabool karta hai jo tauba kare. ''
6440,ham usey Quran hi mein se samajhtey they yahan tak ke aayat (ألهاكم التكاثر‏) nazil hui.
6441,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maanga to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ata farmaya, maine phir maanga aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir ata farmaya, maine phir maanga aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir ata farmaya, phir farmaya ke ye maal aur kabhi-kabhi Sufiyan ne yun bayan kya ke (hakeem (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya) aey hakeem ! ye maal sar-sabz aur khushgawaar nazar aata hai isliye jo shakhs usey nek niyatii (نیتی) se ley usmein barkat hoti hai aur jo laalach ke sath leta hai to uske maal mein barkat nahi hoti balke wo us shakhs jaisa ho jata hai jo khata jata hai lekin uska pet nahi bharta aur uper ka hath nichey ke hath se behtar hai."
6442,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein kon hai jisey apne maal se zyada apne waaris ka maal pyara ho.'' sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham mein koi aisa nahi jisey maal zyada pyara na ho. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya'' phir uska maal wo hai jo usney (maut se) pahley (Allah ke raaste mein kharch) kya aur uske waaris ka maal wo hai jo wo chhod kar maraa .''
6443,"aik roz mein bahar nikla to dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tanha chal rahe they aur aap ke sath koi bhi na tha, Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke is se main samjha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isey pasand nahi farmaaengey ke aap ke sath us waqt koi rahe. isliye main chaand ke saaey main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey-peechhey chalney laga. iske baad aap mudey to mujhey dekha aur malum farmaya kon hai? maine arz kya : abu-Zar! Allah mujhey aap par qurbaan kare. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, abu-Zar! yahan aao. bayan kya ke phir main thodi der tak aap ke sath chalta raha. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo log (duniyaa mein) zyada maal w daulat jama kiye huey hain qiyamat ke din wahi khasaarey mein hongey. siwaey unke jinhein Allah Taala ne maal diya ho aur unhon-ne usey daaein baaein, aagey-peechhey kharch kya ho aur usey bhaley kaamon mein lagaya ho. (abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) bayan kya ke phir thodi der tak main aap ke sath chalta raha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, baith jao. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey aik hamwaar zameen par bitha diya jiske charon taraf patthar they aur farmaya ke haan, us waqt tak baithey raho jab tak main tumharey paas lot aaoon. phir aap pathreelii zameen ki taraf chaley gaey aur nazron se ojhal ho gaey. aap wahan rahe aur der tak wahin rahe. phir maine aap se suna, aap ye kehtey huey tashrif la rahe they '' chahey chori ho, chahey zina ho '' Abu-Zar kehtey hain ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to mujh se sabr nahi ho saka aur maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Nabi ! Allah aap par mujhey qurbaan kare. is pathreelii zameen ke kinarey aap kis se baatein kar rahe they. maine to kisi doosrey ko aap se baat kartey nahi dekhaa? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) they. pathreelii zameen (Harra) ke kinarey wo mujh se miley aur kaha ke apni ummat ko khushkhabri suna do ke jo bhi us haal mein marega ke Allah ke sath kisi cheez ko Sharik na thahraataa ho to wo jannat mein jaeyga maine arz kya : aey Jibraaiil! chahe us ne chori ki ho, zina kya ho? Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha haan, chahe usne sharab hi pi ho. nazar ne bayan kya ke hamein Shoba ne khabar di (kahaa) ham se Habib bin abi saabit, Aamash aur Abdul-Azeez bin rafeea' ne bayan kya, unse Zaid-bin Wahab ne isi tarah bayan kya. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha Abu-Saleh ne jo usi baab mein abu-Darda se riwayat ki hai wo munqata' hai) Abu-Saleh ne abu-Darda se nahi suna (aur sahi nahi hai ham ne ye bayan kar diya taake us hadis ka haal malum ho jaey aur sahi Abu-Zar ki hadis hai (jo uper mazkoor hui ( kisi ne imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se puchha Ata-bin-Yasar ne bhi to ye hadis abu-Darda se riwayat ki hai. unhon-ne kaha wo bhi munqata' hai aur sahi nahi hai. aakhir sahi wahi Abu-Zar ki hadis niklii. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha abu-Darda ki hadis ko chhodo (wo sanad leney ke laaiq nahi hai kyonke wo munqata' hai) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke Abu-Zar ki hadis ka matlab ye hai ke martey waqt aadmi ( لا إله إلا الله ( kahey aur tauheed par khaatma ho (to wo aik na aik din zaroor jannat mein jaeyga chahey kitna hi gunahgaar ho) . kuchh nuskhon mein ye hai) هذا اذا تاب وقال لا إله إلا الله عند الموت ( yani Abu-Zar ki hadis us shakhs ke barey mein hai jo gunah se tauba karey aur martey waqt ( لا إله إلا الله ( kahey ."
6444,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina ke pathreeley ilaqe mein chal raha tha ke Uhud pahaad hamarey samney aa gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya : Abu-Zar ! maine arz kya, hazir hun ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey is se bilkul khushi nahi hogi ke mere paas is Uhud ke barabar sona ho aur is par teen din is tarah guzar jayen ke usmein se aik Dinar bhi baqi reh jaey siwa us thodi si raqam ke jo main qarz ki adaaeygi ke liye chhod dun balke mein usey Allah ke bandon mein is tarah kharch karun apni daain taraf se, baain taraf se aur peechhey se. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaltey rahe, iske baad farmaya, zyada maal jama rakhney waley hi qiyamat ke din muflis hongey siwa us shakhs ke jo us maal ko is-is tarah daain taraf se, baain taraf se aur peechhey se kharch karey aur aisey log kam hain. phir mujh se farmaya, yahin thahrey raho, yahan se us waqt tak na jana jab tak main aa na jaun. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ki taareeki mein chaley gaey aur nazron se ojhal ho gaey. iske baad maine awaz suni jo buland thi. mujhey dar laga ke kahin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko koi dushwari na pesh aa gaee ho. maine aap ki khidmat mein pahunchne ka irada kya lekin aap ka irshad yad aaya ke apni jagah se na hatna , jab tak main na aa jaun. chunanche jab tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif nahi laey main wahan se nahi hataa. phir aap aaey maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! maine aik awaz suni thi, mujhey dar laga lekin phir aap ka irshad yad aaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya kya tum ne suna tha? maine arz kya, ji haan. farmaya ke wo Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) they aur unhon-ne kaha ke aap ki ummat ka jo shakhs is haal mein mar jaey ke usne Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na kya ho to jannat mein jaeyga maine puchha chahe us ne zina aur chori bhi ki ho? unhon-ne kaha haan zina aur chori hi kyon na ki ho."
6445,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar mere paas Uhud pahaad ke barabar bhi sona ho to mujhey usmein khushi hogi ke teen din bhi mujh par is haal mein na guzarney paaein ke usmein se mere paas kuchh bhi baqi bachchey . albatta agar kisi ka qarz door karne ke liye kuchh rakh chhodun to ye aur baat hai.
6446,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''maaldaarii ye nahi hai ke saman zyada ho, balke maaldaarii ye hai ke dil ghanii (maaldaar) ho. ''"
6447,"aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney se guzra to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik doosrey shakhs Abu-Zar-Ghifaarii (Raziallahu anhu) se jo aap ke qareeb baithey huey they, puchha ke us shakhs ( guzrey waale) ke mutaalliq tum kya kehtey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke ye muazzaz logon mein se hai aur Allah ki qism ! ye is qaabil hai ke agar ye paighaame-nikaah bhejey to us se nikah kar diya jaey. agar ye sifarish karey to unki sifarish qabool kar li jaey. bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye sun kar khamosh ho gaey. iske baad aik doosrey sahib guzrey . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse unke mutaalliq bhi puchha ke unke barey mein tumhari kya raey hai? unhon-ne kaha, ya Rasulullah ! ye sahib musalmanon ke ghareeb tabqey se hain aur ye aisey hain ke agar ye nikah ka paigham bhejein to unka nikah na kya jaey, agar ye kisi ki sifarish karein to unki sifarish qabool na ki jaey aur agar kuchh kahein to unki baat na suni jaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske baad farmaya ke Allah ke nazdeek ye pichhlaa mohtaaj shakhs agley maaldaar shakhs se, bhale hi waisey aadmi zameen bhar kar hon, behtar hai."
6448,"ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Allah Taala ki raza hasil karne ke liye hijrat ki. chunanche hamara ajr Allah ke zimme raha. to ham mein se koi to guzar gaya aur apna ajr (is duniya mein) nahi liya. Mus'ab-bin-Umair (Raziallahu anhu)) unhi ( mein se they, wo jange-Uhud ke mauqe par Shahid ho gaey they aur aik chadar chhodi thi (is chadar ka unko kafan diya gaya tha) us chadar se ham agar unka sar dhaktey to unke paon khul jatey aur paon dhaktey to sar khul jata. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke ham unka sar dhak dein aur paon par izkhir ghaas daal dein aur koi ham mein se aisey huey jinke phal khub pakey aur wo mazey se chun chun kar kha rahe hain."
6449,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''maine jannat mein jhanka to usmein rehney waley aksar ghareeb log they aur maine dozakh mein jhanka to uski rehney waaliyaan aksar auratein thin. ''abu-Rijaa ke sath is hadis ko Ayub sakhtiyan aur Auf ne bhi riwayat kya hai aur sakhr bin Juweriya aur Hammad bin najeeh donon is hadis ko abu-Rijaa se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya."
6450,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi mez par khana nahi khaayaa. yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee aur na wafat tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi baareek chapaatii khaaii.
6451,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to mere toshey-khaane mein koi ghalla na tha jo kisi jaandaar ke khaney ke qaabil hota, siwa thodey se jau ke jo mere toshey mein they, main unmein hi se khaatii rahi aakhir uktaa kar jab bahut din ho gaey to maine unhein naapaa to wo khatm ho gaey."
6452,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke Allah ki qism jiske siwa koi maabood nahi main (zamaana nabwi mein) bhook ke maarey zameen par apne pet ke bal let jata tha aur kabhi main bhook ke maarey apne pet par patthar baandha karta tha. aik din mein us rastey par baith gaya jis se sahaba nikaltey they Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) guzrey aur maine unse kitabullah ki aik aayat ke barey mein poochha, mere poochhney ka maqsad sirf ye tha ke wo mujhey kuchh khilaa dein magar wo chaley gaey aur kuchh nahi kya. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) mere paas se guzrey, maine unse bhi Quran Majeed ki aik aayat poochhi aur poochhney ka maqsad sirf ye tha ke wo mujhey kuchh khilaa dein magar wo bhi guzar gaey aur kuchh nahi kya. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) guzrey aur aap ne jab mujhey dekha to aap muskuraa diye aur jo mere dil main aur jo mere chehrey par tha aap ne pehchan liya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, abu-Huraira! maine arz kya labbaik, ya Rasulullah ! farmaya mere sath aa jao aur aap chalney lagey. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey chal diya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar ghar mein tashrif ley gaey. phir maine ijazat chahi aur mujhey ijazat milii. jab aap dakhil huey to aik pyaley mein doodh mila. malum farmaya ke ye doodh kahan se aaya hai? kaha falan ya fulaanii ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye tohfe mein bheja hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, abu-Huraira! maine arz kya labbaik, ya Rasulullah ! farmaya, ahale-suffa ke paas jao aur unhein bhi mere paas bula laao. kaha ke ahale-suffa Islam ke mehmaan hain, wo na kisi ke ghar panah dhoondhtey , na kisi ke maal main aur na kisi ke paas ! jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas sadqa aata to usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhiin ke paas bhej detey aur khud usmein se kuchh na rakhtey. albatta jab aap ke paas tohfa aata to unhein bulwa bhejtey aur khud bhi usmein se kuchh khaatey aur unhein bhi Sharik kartey. chunanche mujhey ye baat na-gawar guzri aur maine sochaa ke ye doodh hai hi kitna ke sarey suffa walon mein taqseem ho, iska haqdaar main tha ke usey pi kar kuchh quwwat hasil karta. jab suffa waley aaeingey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh se farmaaengey aur main unhein usey de doonga . mujhey to shayad us doodh mein se kuchh bhi nahi milega lekin Allah aur uske rasool ki hukm-bardaarii ke siwa koi aur chaara bhi nahi tha. chunanche main unke paas aaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dawat pahunchaaii, wo aagey aur ijazat chaahi. unhein ijazat mil gaee phir wo ghar main apni apni jagah baith gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : abu-Huraira! maine arz kya labbaik , ya Rasulullah ! farmaya lo aur usey un sab haaziriin ko de do. bayan kya ke phir maine piyala pakad liya aur eik-eik ko diye laga. aik shakhs doodh pi kar jab sairaab ho jata to mujhey piyala wapas kar deta phir doosrey shakhs ko deta wo bhi sairaab ho kar peetaa phir piyala mujh ko wapas kar deta aur isi tarah teesra pi kar phir mujhey piyala wapas kar deta. is tarah main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahuncha log pi kar sairaab ho chukey they. aakhir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne piyala pakda aur apne hath par rakh kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri taraf dekha aur muskuraa kar farmaya, abu-Huraira! maine arz kya, labbaik, ya Rasulullah! farmaya, ab main aur tum baqi reh gaey hain. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne sach farmaya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya baith jao aur piyo . main baith gaya aur maine doodh piyaa aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) barabar farmatey rahe ke aur piyo aakhir mujhey kehna padaa, nahi us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath bheja hai, ab bilkul gunjaaish nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, phir mujhey de do, maine piyala Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko de diya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki hamd bayan ki aur bismillaah padh kar bacha hua khud pi gaey."
6453,main sabse pahlaa Arab hun jisne Allah ke rastey mein teer chillaey . ham ne us haal mein waqt guzara hai ke jihad kar rahe hain aur hamarey paas khaney ki koi cheez habla ke patton aur us babool ke siwa khaney ke liye nahi thi aur bakri ki mengniyon ki tarah ham pakhana kiya kartey they. ab ye banu-Asad ke log mujh ko Islam sikhlaa kar durust karna chahtey hain phir to main bilkul bad-naseeb thehra aur mera Sara kya karaya akaarat gaya.
6454,"Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar walon ko Madina aaney ke baad kabhi teen din tak barabar gehun ki roti khaney ke liye nahi mili , yahan tak ki Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Rooh qabz ho gaee."
6455,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke gharaane ne agar kabhi aik din mein 2 martaba khana khaya to zaroor usmein aik waqt sirf khajoorein hoti thin.
6456,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka bistar chamdey ka tha aur is mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi.
6457,"ham Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hotey, unka naan baaii wahin maujood hota (jo rotiyaan pakka pakaa kar deta jaataa) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) logon se kehtey ke khaao, maine kabhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko patlii roti khaatey nahi dekha aur na Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi apni aankh se samoochii bhunii hui bakri dekhi. yahan tak ke aap ka intiqal ho gaya."
6458,"hamarey uper aisa mahina bhi guzar jata tha ke choolha nahi jaltaa tha, sirf khajoor aur pani hota tha, haan agar kabhi kisi jagah se kuchh thoda sa gosht aa jata to usko bhi kha letey they."
6459,"unhon-ne Urwa se kaha, betey! ham 2 mahinon mein teen chaand dekh letey hain aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki beeviyon) ke gharon mein choolha nahi jaltaa tha. maine puchha phir aap log zinda kis cheez par rehti thin ? batlaya ke sirf 2 kali chizon par, khajoor aur pani . haan , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh Ansari padosi they jinke yahan dudhail oontniyan thin wo apne gharon se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye doodh bhej detey aur aap hamein wahi doodh pilaa detey they."
6460,"ham se Abdullah-bin Muhammad ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ham se Muhammad-bin-Fuzail ne bayan kya, unse unke walid ne, unse Umara ne, unse Abu-Zaraa ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne duaa ki ke aey Allaah! aale-Muhammad ko itnii rozii dey ke wo zinda reh sakein."
6461,"maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se poochha, kon si ibadat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zyada pasand thi, farmaya ke jis par hameshgii ho sakey, kaha ke maine puchha aap raat ko tahajjud ke liye Kab uthtey they? batlaya ke jab murgh ki awaz sun letey."
6462,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sabse zyada pasandida wo amal tha jis ko aadmi hamesha karta rahe.
6463,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum se kisi shakhs ko iska amal nijat nahi dila sakega.'' sahaba ne kaha aur aapko bhi nahi ya rasoolullaah? farmaya ''aur mujhey bhi nahi, siwa iske ke Allah Taala mujhey apni rehmat ke saaye mein ley ley. to tum ko chahiye ke durustii ke sath amal karo aur miyaanaa rawii ikhtiyar karo. subah aur Shaam, isi tarah raat ko zara sa chal liya karo aur aetidaal ke sath chala karo manzil maqsud ko pahunch jaogey .''"
6464,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''darmyaanii chaal ikhtiyar karo aur buland parwaazii na karo aur amal kartey raho, tum mein se kisi ka amal usey jannat mein nahi dakhil kar sakega , mere nazdeek sabse pasandida amal wo hai jis par hameshgii ki jaey chahe kam hi kyon na ho.''"
6465,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya kon sa amal Allah ke nazdeek zyada pasandida hai? farmaya ke jis par hameshgii ki jaey, chahe wo thodi hi ho aur farmaya nek kaam karne mein itni hi takleef uthao jitni taqat hai (jo hamesha nibh sakey)."
6466,maine Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : ummul-momeneen! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kyonkar ibadat kya kartey they kya aap ne kuchh khas din khas kar rakhey they? batlaya ke nahi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke amal mein hameshgii hoti thi aur tum mein kon hai jo in amalon ki taqat rakhta ho jinki Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) taqat rakhtey they.
6467,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' dekho jo nek kaam karo theek taur se karo aur had se na badh jao balke iske qareeb raho (beech ki ravish ikhtiyar karo) aur khush raho aur yad rakho ke koi bhi apne amal ki wjah se jannat mein nahi jaeyga sahaba ne arz kya : aur aap bhi nahi ya Rasulullah ! farmaya aur main bhi nahi. siwa iske ke Allah apni maghfirat w rehmat ke saaye mein mujhey dhaank ley. madeenii ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai ke Musa-bin-Aqba ne ye hadis abu-Salma se Abul-Nasar ke waastey se suni hai, abu-Salma ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se. aur Affaan-bin-Muslim ne bayan kya ke ham se Wuhaib ne bayan kya, unse Musa-bin-Aqba ne bayan kya, kaha ke maine abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aur unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''durustii ke sath amal karo aur khush raho.''"
6468,"maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein aik din Namaz padhai, phir member par chadhey aur apne hath se masjid ke qible ki taraf ishara kya aur farmaya ke us waqt jab maine tumhen Namaz padhai to mujhey us diwar ki taraf jannat aur dozakh ki tasweer dikhai gaee maine ( saari umr mein) aaj ki tarah na koi jannat ki si khoobsurat cheez dekhi na dozakh ki si daraawnii , maine aaj ki tarah na koi jannat jaisi khoobsurat cheez dekhi na dozakh jaisi daraawnii cheez ."
6469,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne rehmat ko jis din banaya to uske so hissey kiye aur apne paas unmein se niniyaanwey rakhey. iske baad tamam makhlooq ke liye sirf aik hissey rehmat ka bhejaa. to agar kaafir ko wo tamam raham malum ho jaey jo Allah ke paas hai to wo jannat se naa-ummeed na ho aur agar momin ko wo tamam azab malum ho jayen jo Allah ke paas hain to dozakh se kabhi be-khauf na ho."
6470,"chand Ansari sahaba ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maanga aur jisne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maanga Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey diya, yahan tak ke jo maal aap ke paas tha wo khatm ho gaya. jab sab kuchh khatm ho gaya jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hathon se diya tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo bhi achi cheez mere paas hogi main usey tum se bacha ke nahi rakhta hun. baat ye hai ke jo tum mein (sawaal se) bachta rahega Allah bhi usey ghaib se dega aur jo shakhs dil par zor daal kar sabr karega Allah bhi usey sabr dega aur jo be-parwaah rehna ikhtiyar karega Allah bhi usey be-parwaah kar dega aur Allah ki koi nemat sabr se badh kar tum ko nahi milii."
6471,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) itni Namaz padhtey ke aap ke qadmon mein waram aa jata ya kaha ke aap ke qadam phool jatey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha jata ke aap to bakhshey huey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey hain ke kya main Allah ka shukr-guzar banda na banoon.
6472,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meri ummat ke 70 hazaar log be-hisaab jannat mein jaengey. ye wo log hongey jo jhaad phoonk nahi karatey na shagoon letey hain aur apne rab hi par bharosa rakhtey hain.''
6473,"koi hadis jo aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni ho wo mujhey likh bhejo. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein likha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, aap Namaz se farigh honey ke baad ye dua padhtey لا إله إلا الله ، Mina وحده لا شريك له ، Mina له الملك ، Mina وله الحمد ، Mina وهو على كل شىء قدير ke ''Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi jo tanha hai uska koi Sharik nahi, badhshahat usi ki hai aur tamam ta'reefein usi ke liye hain aur wo har cheez par qudrat rakhney wala hai.'' ye teen martaba padhtey. bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) be-faayda baat cheet karne, zyada sawal karne, maal zaaye karne, apni cheez bacha kar rakhney aur dusron ki maangtey rahney, maaon ki nafarmani karne aur ladkiyon ko zinda dargor karne se mana farmatey they. aur Hushaim se riwayat hai, unhein Abdul-Malik ibne-Umair ne khabar di, kaha ke maine Waraad se suna, wo ye hadis Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey they aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
6474,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' mere liye jo shakhs donon jabdon ke darmyan ki cheez ( zaban (aur donon taangon ke darmyan ki cheez ( sharmgah ( ki zimme-dari dedey mein uske liye jannat ki zimme-dari deta hoon.''
6475,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo koi Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta hai usey chahiye ke achi baat kahey warna khamosh rahe aur jo koi Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta hai wo apne padosi ko takleef na pahunchaaey aur jo koi Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho wo apne mehman ki izzat kare. ''
6476,mere donon kanon ne suna hai aur mere dil ne yad rakha hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha '' mehmani teen din ki hoti hai magar jo lazimi hai wo to poori karo. puchha gaya lazimi kitni hai? farmaya ke aik din aur aik raat aur jo koi Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta hai usey chahiye ke apne mehman ki khaatir karey aur jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta hai usey chahiye ke achi baat kahey warna chup rahe.
6477,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' banda aik baat zaban se nikaaltaa hai aur uske mutaalliq sochtaa nahi (kitnii kufr aur be-adabii ki baat hai) jiski wjah se wo dozakh ke garhey mein itni door gir padta hai jitna maghrib se mashriq door hai.''
6478,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' banda Allah ki raza-mandi ke liye aik baat zaban se nikaaltaa hai usey wo koi ahmiyat nahi deta magar usi ki wjah se Allah uske darjey buland kar deta hai aur aik doosra banda aik aisa kalima zaban se nikaaltaa hai jo Allah ki narazagi ka baais hota hai usey wo koi ahmiyat nahi deta lekin uski wjah se wo jahannam mein chala jata hai.''
6479,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' saat (7) tarah ke log wo hain jinhein Allah Taala apne saaye mein panah dega. (un mein) aik wo shakhs bhi hai jisne tanhai mein Allah ko yad kya to uski aankhon se aansu jari ho gaey. ''
6480,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''pichhlii ummaton mein ka, aik shakhs jisey apne burey amalon ka dar tha. us ne apne ghar walon se kaha ke jab main mar jaun to meri laash reza reza karke garm din mein utha ke dariya mein daal dena. iske ghar walon ne iske sath aisa hi kya phir Allah Taala ne usey jama kya aur us se puchha ke ye jo tum ne kya uski wjah kya hai? us shakhs ne kaha ke parwardigar mujhey is par sirf terey khof ne aamada kya, chunanche Allah Taala ne uski maghfirat farma di."
6481,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pichhli ummaton ke aik shakhs ka zikr farmaya ke Allah Taala ne usey maal w aulad ata farmai thi. farmaya ke jab uski maut ka waqt aaya to usne apne ladkon se poochha, bap ki haisiyat se maine kaisa apne aapko Sabit kya? ladkon ne kaha ke behtreen bap . phir us shakhs ne kaha ke usne Allah ke paas koi neki nahi jama ki hai. Qatada ne ( لم يبتئر ( ki tafseer ( لم يدخر (ke nahi jama ki, se ki hai. aur us ne ye bhi kaha ke agar usey Allah ke huzoor mein pesh kya gaya to Allah Taala usey azab dega (is ne apne ladkon se kaha ke) dekho, jab main mar jaun to meri laash ko jalaa dena aur jab main koila ho jaun to mujhey pees dena aur kisi tez hawa ke din mujhey usmein uda dena. us ne apne ladkon se is par wada liya chunanche ladkon ne uske sath aisa hi kya. phir Allah Taala ne farmaya ke ho jaa. chunanche wo aik mard ki shakl mein khada nazar aaya. phir farmaya, mere bandey! ye jo to ne karaya hai is par tujhey kis cheez ne aamada kya tha? usne kaha ke terey khof ne. Allah Taala ne iska badla ye diya ke is par raham farmaya, maine ye hadis Usman se bayan ki to unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Salman se suna. albatta unhon-ne ye lafz bayan kiye ke ''mujhey dariya mein baha dena ''yaa jaisa ke unhon-ne bayan kya aur Muaz ne bayan kya ke ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne, unhon-ne Aqba se suna, unhon-ne abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
6482,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meri aur jo kuchh kalaamullaah ne mere sath bheja hai uski misal aik aisey shakhs jaisi hai jo apni qaum ke paas aaya aur kaha ke maine (tumhaarey dushman ka ( lashkar apni aankhon se dekha hai aur main waazeh daraane wala hun. to bhaago, bhaago (apni jaan bachaao) is par aik jamat ne uski baat maan li aur raat hi raat itminan se kisi mehfooz jagah par nikal gaey aur nijat paaii. lekin dusri jamat ne usey jhutlaayaa aur dushman ke lashkar ne subah ke waqt achcha unhein aa liya aur tabah kar diya. ''"
6483,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri aur logon ki misal aik aisey shakhs ki hai jisne aag jalaaii, jab uske charon taraf roshni ho gaee to parwaaney aur ye keedey makodey jo aag par girtey hain usmein girney lagey aur aag jalaaney wala unhein usmein se nikalney laga lekin wo iske qaabu mein nahi aaey aur aag mein girtey rahe. isi tarah mein tumhari kamar ko pakad kar aag se tumhen nikaaltaa hon aur tum ho ke usi mein girtey jatey ho."
6484,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' musalman wo hai jo musalmanon ko apni zaban aur hath se ( takleef pahunchne se) mehfooz rakhey aur muhajir wo hai jo un chizon se ruk jaey jis se Allah ne mana kya hai.''
6485,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kya kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar tumhen wo malum ho jaey jo main janta hun to tum hanstey kam aur rotey zyaada.''
6486,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar tumhen wo malum hota jo main janta hun to tum hanstey kam aur rotey zyada .''
6487,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' dozakh khuwaahishaate-nafsaanii se dhak di gaee hai aur jannat mushkilaat aur dushwaariyon se dhakii hui hai.''
6488,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jannat tumharey jootey ke tasmey se bhi zyada tumharey qareeb hai aur isi tarah dozakh bhii.''
6489,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sabse sachcha sher jisey shaair ne kaha hai ye hai ''haan Allah ke siwa tamam cheezein be-buniyaad hain.''
6490,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab tum maine koi shakhs kisi aisey aadmi ko dekhey jo maal aur shakl w sura mein us se badh kar hai to usey aisey shakhs ka dhyaan karna chahiye jo us se kam darje ka hai.''
6491,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik hadeese-qudsi mein farmaya ''Allah taala ne nekiyan aur buraaiyaan muqaddar kar di hain aur phir unhein saaf-saaf bayan kar diya hai. to jisne kisi neki ka irada kya lekin is par amal na kar saka to Allah Taala ne uske liye aik mukammal neki ka badla likha hai aur agar us ne irade ke baad is par amal bhi kar liya to Allah Taala ne uske liye apne yahan das guna se saat so guna tak nekiyan likhi hain aur us se badh kar aur jisne kisi burai ka irada kya aur phir is par amal nahi kya to Allah Taala ne uske liye apne yahan neki likhi hai aur agar us ne irada ke baad is par amal bhi kar liya to apne yahan uske liye aik burai likhi hai.
6492,"tum aisey-aisey amal kartey ho jo tumhari nazar mein baal se zyada baareek hain (tum usey haqeer samajhtey ho, bada gunah nahi samajhtey) aur ham log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein un kaamon ko halaak kar dene wala samajhtey they. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke hadis mein jo lafz (moobiqaat) hai iska mana halaak karne waale."
6493,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko dekha jo mushrekeen se jang mein masroof tha, ye shakhs musalmanon ke saahibe-maal w daulat logon mein se tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar koi chahta hai ke kisi jahannami ko dekhey to wo us shakhs ko dekhey. is par aik sahabi us shakhs ke peechhey lag gaey wo shakhs barabar ladtaa raha aur aakhir zakhmi ho gaya. phir us ne chaha ke jaldi mar jaey. to apni talwaar hi ki dhaar apne seeney ke darmyan rakh kar is par apne aapko daal diya aur talwaar iske shaanon ko cheertii hui nikal gaee (is tarah wo khudkushii karke mar gaya) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke banda logon ki nazar mein ahle-jannat ke kaam karta rehta hai halanke wo jahannam mein se hota hai. aik doosra banda logon ki nazar mein ahale-jahannam ke kaam karta rehta hai halanke wo jannati hota hai aur aamaal ka eitibaar to khaatme par tikaa hua hai."
6494,"sawal kya gaya : aey Allah ke rasool! Muhammad-bin Yusuf ne bayan kya, unse Auzai ne bayan kya, unse Zohri ne bayan kya, unse Ata-bin-Yazeed Lesi ne bayan kya aur unse Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke aik dehati Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur puchha : ya Rasulullah ! kon shakhs sabse achchha hai? farmaya ke wo shakhs jisne apni jaan aur maal ke zariey jihad kya aur wo shakhs jo kisi pahaad ki khoh mein thehra hua apne rab ki ibadat karta hai aur logon ko apni burai se mehfooz rakhta hai. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Zubaidi , Sulaiman-bin Kasir aur Nauman ne Zohri se ki. aur Mamar ne Zohri se bayan kya, unse ata ya Ubaidullah ne, unse Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aur Yunus w ibne- musaafir aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se bayan kya, unse Ata ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kisi sahabi ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne."
6495,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke logon par aik aisa dour aayega jab aik musalman ka sabse behtar maal bhedein hongi wo unhein lekar pahaad ki chotiyon aur barish ki jaghon par chala jaeyga us din wo apne Deen ko lekar fasaadon se dar kar wahan se bhag jaeyga"
6496,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab amanat barbad ki jaey to qiyamat ka intizar karo.'' puchha : ya Rasulullah ! amanat kis tarah barbad ki jaeygi ? farmaya ''jab kaam naa-ahal logon ke sipurd kar diye jayen to qiyamat ka intizar karo.''
6497,"ham se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne do hadisein irshad farmaein . aik ka zuhoor to main dekh chuka hun aur dusri ka muntazir hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya ke amanat logon ke dilon ki gahraaiyon mein utartii hai. phir Quran sharif se, phir hadis sharif se uski mazbootii hoti jati hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se iske uth janey ke mutaalliq irshad farmaya ke aadmi aik neend soey ga aur (usi mein) amanat uske dil se khatm hogi aur us be-Eimaanii ka halka nishan pad jaeyga phir aik aur neend lega ab iska nishan chhaaley ki tarah ho jaeyga jaisey to paon par aik chingaarii (چنگاری) ludhkaaey to zahir mein aik chhaalaa phool aata hai usko phulaa (پھولا) dekhta hai, par andar kuchh nahi hota. phir haal ye ho jaeyga ke subah uth kar log khareed w farokht karengey aur koi shakhs amanat daar nahi hoga, kaha jaeyga ke bani falan mein aik amanat daar shakhs hai. kisi shakhs ke mutaalliq kaha jaeyga ke kitna aqlmand hai, kitna buland hosla hai aur kitna bahaadur hai. halanke uske dil mein raai barabar bhi eman (amaanat) nahi hoga.'' ( Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain) maine aik aisa waqt bhi guzara hai ke main uski parwaa nahi karta tha ke kis se khareed w farokht karta hun. agar wo musalman hota to usko Islam (be-Eimaanii se) roktaa tha. agar wo nasrani hota to uska madadgaar usey roktaa tha lekin ab main falan aur falan ke siwa kisi se khareed w farokht hi nahi karta."
6498,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke logon ki misal oonton ki si hai qareeb hai ke to unmein se aik ko bhi sawari ke qaabil na paaey."
6499,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur maine aap ke siwa kisi ko ye kehtey nahi suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, chunanche main unke qareeb pahuncha to maine suna ke wo keh rahe they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (kisi nek kaam ke nateeje mein) jo shohrat ka taalib ho Allah Taala uski bad-niyati qiyamat ke din sab ko suna dega. isi tarah jo koi logon ko dikhaaney ke liye nek kaam karega Allah bhi qiyamat ke din usko sab logon ko dikhla dega."
6500,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari par aap ke peechhey betha hua tha. siwa kajaawa ke aakhiri hissey ke mere aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darmyan koi cheez haail nahi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey Muaz ! maine arz kya labbaik va sa'deik (وسعدیک) , ya Rasulullah ! phir thodi der Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaltey rahe phir farmaya, aey Muaz ! maine arz kya labbaik va sa'deik (وسعدیک) ya Rasulullah ! phir thodi der mazeed Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaltey rahe. phir farmaya, aey Muaz ! maine arz kya labbaik va sa'deik (وسعدیک) ya Rasulullah ! farmaya, tumhen malum hai ke Allah ka apne bandon par kya haq hai? maine arz kya Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai. farmaya, Allah ka bandon par ye haq hai ke wo Allah hi ki ibadat karein aur uske sath kisi ko Sharik na thehraein . phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thodi der chaltey rahe aur farmaya, aey Muaz-bin-Jabal ! maine arz kya labbaik va sa'deik (وسعدیک) ya Rasulullah ! farmaya, tumhen malum hai ke jab bandey ye kar lein to unka Allah par kya haq hai? maine arz kya Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai. farmaya ke bandon ka Allah par ye haq hai ke wo unhein azab na de."
6501,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik ontni thi (doosri sanad) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha aur mujh se Muhammad-bin salam ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko fazari ne aur abu-Khalid Ahmar ne khabar di, unhein Humaid taweel ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik ontni thi jiska naam azbaa tha (koii janwar daud mein) us se aagey nahi badh paata tha. phir aik dehati apne oont par Sawar ho kar aaya aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ontni se aagey badh gaya. musalmaanon par ye mamla bada sakht guzra aur kehney lagey ke afsos azbaa peechhey reh gaee. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke Allah Taala ne apne uper ye lazim kar liya hai ke jab duniya mein wo kisi cheez ko badhata hai to usey wo ghataataa bhii hai."
6502,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala farmata hai ke jisne mere kisi wali se dushmanii ki usey meri taraf se ea'laane jang hai aur mera banda jin jin ibaadaton se mera qurb hasil karta hai aur koi ibadat mujh ko is se zyada pasand nahi hai jo maine is par farz ki hai (yani faraaiz mujh ko bahut pasand hain jaisey namaaz, roza, Haj, zakaat) aur mera banda farz ada karne ke baad nafl ibaadatein karke mujh se itna nazdeek ho jata hai ke main us se mohabbat karne lag jata hun. phir jab main us se mohabbat karne lag jata hun to main us-ka kaan bin jata hun jis se wo sunta hai, uski aankh bin jata hun jis se wo dekhta hai, uska hath bin jata hun jis se wo pakadta hai, uska paon bin jata hun jis se wo chalta hai aur agar wo mujh se mangta hai to main usey deta hun agar wo kisi dushman ya shaitan se meri panah mangta hai to main usey mehfooz rakhta hun aur main jo kaam karna chahta hun usmein mujhey itna tardduud nahi hota jitna ke mujhey apne momin bandey ki jaan nikalney mein hota hai. wo to maut ko  jismaanii takleef ki wajah se pasand nahi karta aur mujh ko bhi usey takleef dena bura lagta hai."
6503,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main aur qiyamat itney nazdeek-nazdeek bhejey gaey hain aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni do ungliyon ke ishara se (is nazdiiki (نزدیکی) ko) bataya phir un donon ko phailaayaa.''
6504,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main aur qiyamat in donon (ungliyon) ki tarah (nazdeek-nazdeek) bhejey gaey hain.''
6505,aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main aur qiyamat in do ki tarah bhejey gaey hain. aap ki murad do ungliyon se thii.'' Abu-Bakar bin Ayash ke sath is hadis ko Israel ne bhi abu-Haseen se riwayat kya hai.
6506,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim na hogi jab tak suraj maghrib se na niklega . jab suraj maghrib se niklega aur log dekh lengey to sab eman ley aaeingey, yahi wo waqt hoga jab kisi ko uska eman nafa nahi dega jo is se pahley eman na laya hoga ya jisne eman ke baad amal khair na kya ho. isliye qiyamat aa jaeygi aur do aadmi kapda darmyan mein (khareed w farokht ke liye) phailaey huey hongey. abhi khareed w farokht bhi nahi hui hogi aur na unhon-ne usey lapeta hi hoga (ke qiyamat qaaim ho jaeygi) aur qiyamat us haal mein qaaim ho jaeygi ke aik shakhs apni ontni ka doodh lekar aa raha hoga aur usey pi bhi nahi sakega aur qiyamat us haal mein qaaim ho jaeygi ke aik shakhs apna hauz taiyaar kara raha hoga aur iska pani bhi na pi paaey ga. qiyamat us haal mein qaaim ho jaeygi ke aik shakhs apna luqma apne munh ki taraf uthaaeyga aur usey khaney bhi na paaey ga.''"
6507,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs Allah se milney ko mahboob rakhta hai, Allah bhi us se milney ko mahboob rakhta hai aur jo Allah se milney ko pasand nahi karta hai Allah bhi us se milney ko pasand nahi kartaa.'' aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kuchh beeviyon ne arz kya ke marnaa to ham bhi nahi pasand kartey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ke milney se maut murad nahi hai balke baat ye hai ke emaandaar aadmi ko jab maut aati hai to usey Allah ki khushnoodii aur uske yahan uski izzat ki khushkhabri di jati hai. us waqt momin ko koi cheez us se zyada azeez nahi hoti jo iske aagey (Allah se mulaqat aur uski raza aur jannat ke husool ke liye) hoti hai, isliye wo Allah se mulaqat ka khaahishmand ho jata hai aur Allah bhi uski mulaqat ko pasand karta hai aur jab kaafir ki maut ka waqt qareeb aata hai to usey Allah ke azab aur uski saza ki bashaarat di jati hai, us waqt koi cheez iske dil mein us se zyada na-gawar nahi hoti jo iske aagey hoti hai. wo Allah se ja milney ko na-pasand karne lagta hai, isliye Allah bhi us se milney ko na-pasand karta hai. Abu-Dawood Tiyalisi aur Amr-bin marzooq ne us hadis ko Shoba se mukhtesar taur (مختصراً) per riwayat kya hai aur Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne, unse zaraarah  (زرارہ) bin abi ufa'a ne, unse Sad ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya."
6508,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs Allah se milney ko pasand karta hai Allah bhi us se milney ko pasand karta hai aur jo shakhs Allah se milney ko na-pasand karta hai Allah bhi us se milney ko na-pasand karta hai.''
6509,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab aap khaasey tandurust they farmaya tha kisi Nabi ki us waqt tak Rooh qabz nahi ki jati jab tak jannat mein uske rehney ki jagah usey dikhaa na di jati ho aur phir usey (duniyaa ya aakhirat ke liye) ikhtiyar diya jata hai. phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar huey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sar Mubarak meri raan par tha to aap par thodi der ke liye ghashii chhaa gaee, phir jab aapko hosh aaya to aap chhat ki taraf tak-takii (ٹکٹکی) laga kar dekhney lagey. phir farmaya (اللهم الرفيق الأعلى) maine kaha ke ab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein tarjeeh nahi de saktey aur main samajh gaee ke ye wahi hadis hai jo aap ne aik martaba irshad farmai thi. rawi ne bayan kya ke ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aakhiri kalima tha jo aap ne apni zabaane Mubarak se ada farmaya yani ye irshad ke (اللهم الرفيق الأعلى) yani ya Allah ! mujh ko buland doston ka sath pasand hai."
6510,"unhein Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghulam abu-Amr-zakwaan ne khabar di ke Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) kaha karti thin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki wafat ke waqt) aap ke samney aik bada pani ka piyala rakha hua tha jis mein pani tha. ye umr ko shubeh hua ke handi ka koondaa tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna hath us bartan mein daltey aur phir us hath ko apne chehra par maltey aur farmatey Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, bila shubah maut mein takleef hoti hai, phir aap apna hath utha kar farmaney lagey (في الرفيق الأعلى) yahan tak ke aap ki Rooh Mubarak qabz ho gaee aur aap ka hath jhuk gaya."
6511,kuch deihaatii jo nangey paon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aatey they aur aap se malum kartey they ke qiyamat Kab aaeygii? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unmein se kam Umr waley ko dekh kar farmaney lagey ke agar ye bachcha zinda raha to iske budhapey se pahley tum par tumhari qiyamat aa jaeygi. Hisham ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad (qiyamat se) unki maut thi.
6512,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb se log aik janaaza lekar guzrey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (مستريح) ya (مستراح) hai yani usey aaraam mil gaya, ya us se aaraam mil gaya. sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ''المستریح او المستراح منہ'' ka kya matlab hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke momin banda duniya ki mashaqqaton aur takleefon se Allah ki rehmat mein nijat pa jata hai wo (مستريح) hai aur (مستراح منہ) wo hai ke faajir (badkaar) bandey se Allah ke bandey, shahar, darakht aur chaupaaey sab aaraam pa jatey hain."
6513,aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye marney wala ya to aaraam paaney wala hai ya doosrey bandon ko aaraam dene wala hai.
6514,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa  ''maiyat ke sath teen cheezein chaltii hain do to wapas aa jati hain sirf aik kaam uske sath reh jata hai, iske saath, iske ghar waale, iska maal aur iska a'mal chalta hai iske ghar waley aur maal to wapas aa jata hai aur iska a'mal iske sath baqi reh jata hai.''"
6515,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa  ''jab tum mein se koi martaa hai to subah w Sham (jab tak wo barzakh mein hai) uske rehney ki jagah usey har roz dikhai jati hai ya dozakh ho ya jannat aur kaha jata hai ke ye terey rehney ki jagah hai yahan tak ke to uthaya jaey (yani qiyamat ke din tak).''
6516,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo log mar gaey unko bura na kaho kyonke jo kuchh unhon-ne aagey bheja tha uske paas wo khud pahunch chukey hain, unhon-ne burey bhaley (بھلے) jo bhi a'mal kiye they waisaa badla pa liyaa.''"
6517,do aadmiyon ne aapas mein gali galoch ki. jin mein se aik musalman tha aur doosra Yahudi tha. musalman ne kaha ke us parwardigar ki qism jisne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tamam jahan par paakiizaa kya. Yahudi ne kaha ke us parwardigar ki qism jisne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko tamam jahan par paakiizaa kya. rawi ne bayan kya ke musalman Yahudi ki baat sun kar khafa ho gaya aur uske munh par aik tamaancha raseed kya. wo Yahudi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apna aur musalman ka Sara waqia bayan kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa  ''dekho Musa (Alaihissalam) par mujh ko fazeelat mat do kyonke qiyamat ke din aisa hoga ke soour phoonktey hi tamam log behosh ho jaeinge aur main sabse pahlaa shakhs hunga jisey hosh aayega . main kya dekhunga ke Musa (Alaihissalam) arsh ilahi ka kouna (کونہ) thaamey huey hain. mujhey nahi malum ki Musa (Alaihissalam) bhi un logon mein hongey jo behosh huey they aur phir mujh se pahley hi hosh mein aagey they ya unmein se hongey jinhein Allah Taala ne us se mustashnaa (apwaad) kar diyaa.''
6518,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke be-hoshii ke waqt tamam log behosh ho jaeinge aur sabse pahley uthney wala mein hunga . us waqt Musa (Alaihissalam) arsh ilahi ka kounaa (کونہ) thaamey hongey. ab main nahi janta ke wo behosh bhi hongey ya nahi. us hadis ko Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya hai.
6519,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala zameen ko apni muththii mein ley lega aur aasmanon ko apne daain hath mein lapet lega , phir farmaeyga ke ab main hun baadshaah, aaj zameen ke badshah kahan gaey?''"
6520,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din saari zameen aik roti ki tarah ho jaeygi jisey Allah Taala ahle-jannat ki mezbaanii ke liye apne hath se ultey-paltey ga jis tarah tum dastar-khuwaan par roti lahraatey phiraatey ho. phir aik Yahudi aaya aur bola : abul-Qaasim ! tum par Rehman barkat nazil karey kya main tumhen qiyamat ke din ahle-jannat ki sabse pehli mehmaan-nawaazii ke barey mein khabar na dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kyon nahi. to usne (bhi yahii) kaha ke saari zameen aik roti ki tarah ho jaeygi jaisa ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamari taraf dekha aur muskuraaey jis se aap ke aagey ke daant dikhai dainey lagey. phir (is ne) khud hi puchha kya main tumhen iske saalan ke mutaalliq khabar na dun? (phir khud hi) bola ke unka saalan      (بالام ونون) hoga. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye kya cheez hai? usne kaha ke bail aur machhli jiski kalejii ke sath ziyaadaa charbi ke hissey ko sattar (70) hazaar aadmi khaaengey."
6521,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din logon ka hashr safaid w surkhi aamez zameen par hoga jaisey maidey ki roti saaf w safaid hoti hai. us zameen par kisi (cheez) ka koi nishan na hoga.''"
6522,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''logon ka hashr teen firqon mein hoga (eik firqey waale) log dilchasbii karne waaley, oosii ke sath darney waley hongey. (doosraa firqa aisey logon ka hoga ke) aik oont par do aadmi sawar hongey kisi oont par teen hongey, kisi oont par char hongey aur kisi par dus hongey aur baqi logon ko aag jama karegi (ahaley shirk ka ye tesraa firqa hoga) jab wo qailula karengey to aag bhi unke sath thahrii hogi jab wo raat guzaarein gey to aag bhi unke sath wahan thahrii hogi jab wo subah karengey to aag bhi subah ke waqt wahan maujood hogi aur jab wo Sham (Syria) karengey to aag bhi Sham ke waqt unke sath maujood hogi. ''"
6523,"aik sahabi ne kaha, aey Allah ke Nabi ! qiyamat mein kaafiron ko unke chehrey ke bal kis tarah hashr kya jaeyga Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo zaat jisne unhein duniya mein do paon par challaayaa usey is par qudrat nahi hai ke qiyamat ke din unhein chehrey ke bal chala de. Qat'ada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke zaroor hai, hamarey rab ki izzat ki qasam, beshak wo munh ke bal chala sakta hai."
6524,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum Allah se qiyamat ke din nangey paaun, nangey badan aur paidal chal kar bin khatna milo-gey. '' Sufiyan ne kaha ke ye hadis un (nau (9) ya dus hadeeson) mein se hai jinke mutaalliq ham samajhtey hain ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khud unko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna."
6525,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke aap member par khutbey mein farma rahe they ke tum Allah Taala se us haal mein milo gey ke nangey paaun, nangey jism aur baghair khatna ho gey."
6526,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein khutba dene ke liye khadey huey aur farmaya ''tum log qiyamat ke din is haal mein jama kiye jaogey ke nangey paon aur nangey jism hogey. jaisa ke Allah Taala ne farmaya ke ''jis tarah ham ne shuru mein paida kya tha isi tarah lota dengey. '' aur tamam makhlooqat mein sabse pahley jisey kapda pahnaayaa jaeyga wo Ibrahim hongey aur meri ummat ke bahut se log laey jaeinge jinke aamaal naamey baaein hath mein hongey. main is par kahunga : aey mere rab! ye to mere sathi hain. Allah Taala farmaeyga tumhen malum nahi ke unhon-ne tumharey baad kya-kya naii-naii bad-duaa nikaalii thin. us waqt main bhi wahi kahunga jo nek bandey (Eisaa (Alaihissalam) ( ne kaha ( وكنت عليهم شهيدا ما دمت فيهم‏ (ke '' ya Allah ! main jab tak unmein maujood raha us waqt tak mein un par gawah tha.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan kya ke Farishtey ( mujh se) kahengey ke ye log hamesha apni eidiyon ke bal phirtey hi rahe (murtad hotey rahe ( .
6527,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum nangey paaun, nangey jism, bila khatna ke uthaey jaogey. ''Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) farmati hain ke is par maine puchha : ya Rasulullah ! to kya mard auratein aik doosrey ko dekhtey hongey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us waqt mamla us se kahin zyada sakht hoga, iska khayal bhi koi nahi kar sakega."
6528,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik kheme mein they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum is par razi ho ke ahle-jannat ka aik chothai raho ? ham ne kaha ke ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum is par razi ho ke ahle-jannat ka tum aik tehai raho ? ham ne kaha ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum is par razi ho ke ahle-jannat ka tum aadhey raho? ham ne kaha ji haan. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai, mujhey ummeed hai ke tum log ( ummat Muslima ( ahle-jannat ka hissa hogey aur aisa isliye hoga ke jannat mein farmaanbardaar nafs ke ilawa aur koi dakhil na hoga aur tum log shirk karne walon ke darmyan ( tadaad mein) is tarah hogey jaisey siyah bail ke jism par safaid baal hotey hain ya jaisey surkh ke jism par aik siyah baal ho."
6529,qiyamat ke din sabse pahley Adam (Alaihissalam) ko pukara jaeyga phir unki nasl unko dekhegii to kaha jaeyga ke ye tumharey buzurg dada Adam hain. ( pukarney par) wo kahengey ke labbaik w sa'daik . Allah Taala farmaeyga ke apni nasl mein se dozakh ka hissa nikaal lo. Adam (Alaihissalam) arz karengey aey parwardigar ! kitnon ko nikaalun ? Allah Taala farmaeyga feesad ( ninyaanwe feesad dozakhi aik jannati ( . sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! jab ham mein so mein ninyaanwe nikal diye jayen to phir baqi kya reh jaeinge ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tamam ummaton mein meri ummat itni hi tadaad mein hogi jaisey siyah bail ke jism par safaid baal hotey hain.
6530,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala farmaeyga, aey Adam ! Adam (Alaihissalam) kahengey hazir hun, farmaan- bardaar hun aur har bhalai terey hath mein hai. Allah Taala farmaeyga jo log jahannam mein daley jaeinge unhein nikaal lo. Adam (Alaihissalam) poochhein gey jahannam mein daley janey waley log kitney hain? Allah Taala farmaeyga ke har aik hazaar mein se nau (9) sou ninyaanwe . yahi wo waqt hoga jab bachchey gham se boodhey ho jaeinge aur haamla auratein apna hamal gira dein gii aur tum logon ko nashey ki haalat mein dekhogey, halanke wo waqei nashey ki haalat mein na hongey balke Allah ka azab sakht hoga. sahaba ko ye baat bahut sakht malum hui to unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! phir ham mein se wo (khush naseeb) shakhs kon hoga? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen khushkhabri ho, aik hazaar yaajooj maajooj ki qaum se hongey aur tum mein se wo aik jannati hoga phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, mujhey ummeed hai ke tum log ahle-jannat ka aik tehai hissey hogey . rawi ne bayan kya ke ham ne is par Allah ki hamd bayan ki aur uski takbeer kahi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai mujhey ummeed hai ke aadha hissey ahle-jannat ka tum log ho gey. tumhari misal dusri ummaton ke muqaabley mein aisi hai jaisey kisi siyah bail ke jism par safaid baalon ki (ma'moolii ta'daad) hoti hai ya wo safaid dagh jo gadhey ke aagey ke paon par hota hai."
6531,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( يوم يقوم Naas لرب العالمين‏ ( ki tafseer mein farmaya ke tum mein se har koi sarey jahaanon ke parwardigar ke aagey khada hoga is haal mein ke uska paseena kanon ki lo tak pahuncha hua hoga.
6532,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din log pasiney mein sharaabor ho jaeinge aur haalat ye ho jaeygi ke tum mein se har kisi ka paseena zameen par 70 hath tak phail jaeyga aur munh tak pahunch kar kanon ko chhooney lagega.''
6533,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sabse pahley jis cheez ka faisla logon ke darmyan hoga wo nahaq khoon ke badla ka hoga.''
6534,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne apne kisi bhai par zulm kya ho to usey chahiye ke us se (is duniya mein) maaf kara ley. isliye ke aakhirat mein rupye-paisey nahi hongey. us se pahley ( maaf kara ley (ke uske bhai ke liye uski nekiyon mein se haq dilaya jaeyga aur agar uske paas nekiyan na hongi to us ( mazloom ( bhai ki buraaiyaan is par daal di jaaeingii.''
6535,"us aayat ke barey main (ونزعنا ما في صدورهم من غل‏) kahaa ke ham se Saeed ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne bayan kya, unse abu-mutwakkil naajii ne aur unse Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''momineen jahannam se chhutkara pa jaeinge lekin dozakh aur jannat ke darmyan aik pul par unhein rok liya jaeyga aur phir aik ke doosrey par un mazaalim ka badla liya jaeyga jo duniya mein unke darmyan aapas mein huey they aur jab kaat-chhaant kar li jaeygi aur safaaii ho jaeygi tab unhein jannat mein dakhil honey ki ijazat milegii. to us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai ! jannatiyon mein se har koi jannat main apne ghar ko duniya ke apne ghar ke muqable mein zyada behtar tareeqey par pehchan lega.''"
6536,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jiske hisab mein khod-kured ki gaee usko zaroor azab hoga.'' wo kehti hain ke maine arz kya : kya Allah Taala ka ye farman nahi hai) فسوف يحاسب حسابا يسيرا‏ ( '' phir an-qareeb unse halka hisab liya jaaeyga.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is se murad sirf peshii hai.
6537,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jis shakhs se bhi qiyamat ke din hisab liya gaya to wo halaak hua. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya Allah Taala ne khud nahi farmaya hai) فأما من أوتي كتابه بيمينه * فسوف يحاسب حسابا يسيرا‏ (ke '' to jiska naamaae-aa'maal iske daain hath mein diya gaya to an-qareeb us se aik aasan hisab liya jaaeyga.'' is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to sirf peshii hogi. ( Allah rabbul-izzat ke kehney ka matlab ye hai ke) qiyamat ke din jiske bhi hisab mein khod kured ki gaee usko azab yaqeeni hoga.
6538,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke qiyamat ke din kaafir ko laya jaeyga aur us se puchha jaeyga ke tumhara kya khayal hai ke agar zameen bhar kar tumharey paas sona ho to kya sab ko (apni nijat ke liye) fidye mein de doge? wo kahega ke haan, to us waqt us se kaha jaeyga ke tum se us se bahut aasan cheez ka (duniyaa mein) mutalba kya gaya tha."
6539,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein har-har fard se Allah Taala qiyamat ke din is tarah kalam karega ke Allah ke aur bandey ke darmyan koi tarjuman nahi hoga. phir wo dekhega to iske aagey koi cheez nazar nahi aaeygi. phir wo apne samney dekhega aur uske samney aag hogi. to tum mein se jo shakhs bhi chahey ke wo aag se bachey to wo Allah ki raah mein khair khairat karta rahe, chahe khajoor ke aik tukdey ke zariey hi mumkin ho."
6540,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jahannam se bacho, phir aap ne chehra pher liya, phir farmaya ke jahannam se bacho aur phir uske baad chehra Mubarak pher liya, phir farmaya jahannam se bacho . teen martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa hi kya. ham ne us se ye khayal kya ke aap jahannam dekh rahe hain. phir farmaya ke jahannam se bacho chahe khajoor ke aik tukdey hi ke zariey ho sakey aur jisey ye bhi na miley to usey ( logon mein) kisi achi baat kehney ke zariey se hi (jahannam se) bchney ki koshish karni chahiye"
6541,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere samney ummatein pesh ki gain kisi Nabi ke sath poori ummat guzri , kisi Nabi ke sath chand aadmi guzrey, kisi Nabi ke sath das aadmi guzrey , kisi Nabi ke sath panch aadmi guzrey aur koi Nabi tanha guzraa. phir maine dekha to insanon ki aik bahut badi jamat door se nazar aai. maine Jibraeel se puchha kya ye meri ummat hai? unhon-ne kaha nahi balke ufuq ki taraf dekho . maine dekha to aik bahut zabardast jamat dikhai di. farmaya ke ye hai aap ki ummat aur ye jo aagey-aagey 70 hazaar ki tadaad hai un logon se hisab na liya jaeyga aur na un par azab hoga. maine puchha : aisa kyon hoga? unhon-ne kaha ke uski wjah ye hai ke ye log dagh nahi lagwaatey they. dam-jhaad nahi karwatey they, shagoon nahi letey they, apne rab par bharosa kartey they. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf Ukaasha-bin-Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) uth kar badhey aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! dua farmaein ke Allah Taala mujhey bhi un logon mein kar de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai ke aey Allah ! unhein bhi unmein se kar de. iske baad aik aur sahabi khadey huey aur arz kya ke mere liye bhi dua farmaein ke Allah Taala mujhey bhi unmein se kar de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Ukasha usmein tum se aagey badh gaey."
6542,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat ki aik jamat jannat mein dakhil hogi jiski tadaad 70 hazaar hogi. unke chehrey is tarah roshan hongey jaisey chaudahween raat ka chaand roshan hota hai. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke is par ukaasha-bin-Mohsin Asadi (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey, apni dhaarii daar kamlii jo unke jism par thi, uthatey huey arz kya : ya Rasulullah! Allah Taala se dua kijiye ke mujhey bhi unmein se kar de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki ke aey Allaah! unhein bhi unmein se kar de. iske baad aik aur sahabi khadey huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! dua kijiye ke Allah mujhey bhi unmein se kar de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Ukasha tum se aagey badh gaey."
6543,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jannat mein meri ummat ke 70 hazaar ya saat (7) laakh ( rawi ko unmein se kisi aik tadaad mein shak tha) aadmi is tarah dakhil hongey ke kuchh log kuchh ko pakdey huey hongey aur is tarah unmein ke agley pichhley sab jannat mein dakhil ho jaeinge aur unke chehrey chaudahwiin raat ke chaand ki tarah roshan hongey.''
6544,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab ahle-jannat jannat main aur ahale-jahannam jahannam mein dakhil ho jaeinge to aik awaz dene wala unke darmyan khada ho kar pukaarega ke aey jahannam waalo! ab tumhen maut nahi aaeygii aur aey jannat waalo! tumhen bhi maut nahi aaeygii balke hamesha yahin rehna hoga.''
6545,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ahle-jannat se kaha jaeyga ke aey ahle-jannat ! hamesha (tumhein yahin ( rehna hai, tumhen maut nahi aaeygii aur ahale-dozakh se kaha jaeyga ke aey dozakh waalo! hamesha (tum ko yahin ( rehna hai, tum ko maut nahi aaeygi.''"
6546,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan kya ke maine jannat mein jhank kar dekha to wahan rehney waley aksar ghareeb log they aur maine jahannam mein jhank kar dekha (shab meraaj mein) to wahan auratein thin.
6547,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main jannat ke darwazey par khada hua to wahan aksar dakhil hone-waale mohtaaj log they aur mehnat mazdoorii karne waley they aur maaldaar log aik taraf rokey gaey hain, unka hisab leney ke liye baqi hai aur jo log dozakhi they wo to dozakh ke liye bhej diye gaey aur maine jahannam ke darwazey par khadey ho kar dekha to usmein aksar dakhil honey wali auratein thiin.''"
6548,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab ahle-jannat jannat mein chaley jaeinge aur ahale-dozakh dozakh mein chaley jaeinge to maut ko laya jaeyga aur usey jannat aur dozakh ke darmyan rakh kar zabah kar diya jaeyga phir aik awaz dene wala awaz dega ke aey jannat waalo! tumhen ab maut nahi aaeygii aur aey dozakh waalo! tumhen bhi ab maut nahi aaeygi. is baat se jannati aur zyada khush ho jaeinge aur jahannami aur zyada ghamgeen ho jaaengey.''
6549,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ahle-jannat se farmaeyga ke aey jannat waalo! jannati jawab dengey ham hazir hain aey hamarey parwardigaar! teri khush-naseebi hasil karne ke liye. Allah Taala poochhega kya ab tum log khush huey ? wo kahengey ab bhi bhala ham razi na hongey kyonke ab to , tu ney hamein wo sab kuchh de diya jo apni makhlooq ke kisi aadmi ko nahi diya. Allah Taala farmaeyga ke main tumhen is se bhi behtar cheez doonga . jannati kahengey aey rab! is se behtar aur kya cheez hogi ? Allah Taala farmaeyga ke ab main tumharey liye apni raza mandi ko hamesha ke liye daaimii kar doonga yani iske baad kabhi tum par naraz nahi hoonga."
6550,"Haarisa-bin-Suraaqa (Raziallahu anhu) badr ki ladai mein Shahid ho gaey. wo us waqt nau-umr they, to unki walida Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaein aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aapko malum hai ke Harisa se mujhey kitni mohabbat thi, (aap mujhey bataaein) agar wo jannat mein hai to main sabr kar loongii aur sabr par sawab ki ummeedwaar rahoongii aur agar koi aur baat hai to aap dekhengey ke main uske liye kya karti hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke afsos kya tum paagal ho gaee ho? jannat aik hi nahi hai, bahut si jannatein hain aur wo ( Harisa ( jannatul-firdaus mein hai."
6551,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kaafir ke donon shaanon ke darmyan tez chalney waley ke liye teen din ki masafat ka fasla hoga.''
6552,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jannat mein aik darakht hai jiske saaye mein sawar 100 saal tak chalney ke baad bhi usey tay nahi kar sakega. ''
6553,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jannat mein aik darakht hoga jiske saaye mein umda aur tez raftaar ghodey par Sawar shakhs 100 saal tak chalta rahega aur phir bhi usey tay na kar sakega. ''
6554,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meri ummat mein 70 hazaar ya saat (7) laakh aadmi jannat mein jaengey. '' rawi ko shak hua ke Sehal se kon si tadaad bayan hui thi, '' (wo jannat mein is tarah dakhil hongey ke) wo aik doosrey ko thaamey huey hongey. unka pahlaa abhi andar dakhil na honey paaeyga ke jab tak aakhiri bhi dakhil na ho jaey. unke chehrey chaudahwiin raat ke chaand ki tarah roshan hongey.''"
6555,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jannat waley (apne uper ke darjon ke) baalaakhaanon ko is tarah dekhengey jaisey tum aasman mein sitaron ko dekhtey ho.''
6556,aur is mein wo us lafz ka izafa kartey they ke ''jaisey tum mashriqii aur maghribii kinaron mein doobtey sitaron ko dekhtey ho. ''
6557,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala qiyamat ke din dozakh ke sabse kam azab paaney waley se poochhega agar tumhen poori zameen ki saari cheezein muyassar hon to kya tum unko fidye mein (is azab se nijat paaney ke liye) de doge, wo kahega ke haan! Allah Taala farmaeyga ke maine tum se us se bhi Sehal cheez ka us waqt mutalba kya tha jab tum Adam (Alaihissalam) ki peeth mein they ke mere sath kisi ko Sharik na karna lekin tum ne ( tauheed ka ( inkar kya aur na maanaa aakhir shirk hi kya.''"
6558,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kuchh log dozakh se shafaat ke zariey niklengey maano ke) ثعارير ( hon.'' Hammad kehtey hain ke maine Amr-bin-Dinar se puchha ke) ثعارير ( kya cheez hai? unhon-ne kaha ke is se murad chhoti kakdiyaan hain aur hua ye tha ke aakhir umr mein Amr-bin-Dinar ke daant gir gaey they. Hammad kehtey hain ke maine Amr-bin-Dinar se kaha : aey abu-Muhammad ! (ye Amr-bin-Dinar ki kunniyat hai) kya aap ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se ye suna hai? unhon-ne bayan kya ke yahan maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jahannam se shafaat ke zariey log niklengey? unhon-ne kaha haan beshak suna hai."
6559,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''eik jamat jahannam se niklegii iske baad ke jahannam ki aag ne unko jalaa daala hoga aur phir wo jannat mein dakhil hongey. ahle-jannat unko (jahannamiyon) ke naam se yad karengey. ''
6560,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab ahle-jannat jannat main aur ahale-jahannam jahannam mein dakhil ho chukengey to Allah Taala farmaeyga ke jiske dil mein raai ke daane ke barabar bhi eman ho to usey dozakh se nikaal lo. us waqt aisey log nikaley jaeinge aur wo us waqt jal kar koiley ki tarah ho gaey hongey. iske baad unhein ''nehre-hayaat'' (zindagii bakhsh dariya ( mein daala jaeyga us waqt wo is tarah taro-taazaa ho jaeinge jis tarah sailaab ki jagah par koode-karkat ka daana (usi raat ya din mein) ug aata hai ya rawi ne kaha ( حميل السيل (ke bajaey) ( حمية السيل ( kaha hai. yani jahan sailaab ka zor ho aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tum ne dekha nahi ke us daane se zard rang ka liptaa hua baa-raunaq paudaa ugtaa hai.
6561,"maine Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat ke din azab ke eitibaar se sabse kam wo shakhs hoga jiske donon qadmon ke nichey aag ka angaara rakha jaeyga aur uski wjah se uska dimagh khol raha hoga."
6562,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat ke din dozkhiyon mein azab ke eitibaar se sabse halka azab paaney wala wo shakhs hoga jiske donon pairon ke nichey 2 angaarey rakh diye jaeinge jinki wjah se uska dimagh khol raha hoga jis tarah handi aur ketli josh khaatii hai."
6563,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jahannam ka zikr kya aur rukh pher liya aur us se panah maangii. phir jahannam ka zikr kya aur rukh pher liya aur us se panah mangi . iske baad farmaya ke dozakh se bacho sadqa de kar chahe khajoor ke aik tukdey hi ke zariey ho sakey, jisey ye bhi na miley usey chahiye ke achi baat keh kar."
6564,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aap ke chacha abu-Taalib ka zikr kya gaya tha, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mumkin hai qiyamat ke din meri shafaat unke kaam aa jaey aur unhein jahannam mein takhnon tak rakha jaey jis se unka bheja kholtaa rahega."
6565,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala qiyamat ke din logon ko jama karega. us waqt log kahengey ke agar ham apne rab ke huzoor mein kisi ki shafaat ley jayen to nafa bakhsh Sabit ho sakti hai. mumkin hai ham apni is haalat se nijat pa jaaein. chunanche log Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey aur arz karengey aap hi wo buzurg Nabi hain jinhein Allah Taala ne apne hath se banaya aur aap ke andar apni chhipaaii hui Rooh phoonki aur farishton ko hukm diya to unhon-ne aapko sajda kya, aap hamarey rab ke huzoor mein hamari shafaat karein. wo kahengey ke main to is laaiq nahi hun, phir wo apni khata ko yad karengey aur kahengey ke Nuh ke paas jao, wo sabse pahley rasool hain jinhein Allah Taala ne bhejaa. log Nuh (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey lekin wo bhi yahi jawab dengey ke main us laaiq nahi hun. wo apni khata ka zikr karengey aur kahein ke tum Ibrahim ke paas jao jinhein Allah Taala ne apna khaleel banaya tha. log unke paas aaeingey lekin ye bhi yahi kahengey ke main is laaiq nahi hun, apni khata ka zikr karengey aur kahengey ke tum log Musa ke paas jao jin se Allah Taala ne kalam kya tha. log Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaeinge lekin wo bhi yahi jawab dengey ke main is laaiq nahi hun, apni khata ka zikr karengey aur kahengey ke Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao . log Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaaeinge, lekin ye bhi kahengey ke main is laaiq nahi hun, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao kyonke unke tamam agley pichhley gunah maaf kar diye gaey hain. chunanche log mere paas aaeingey. us waqt main apne rab se ( shafaat ki) ijazat chaahoonga aur sajde mein gir jaaunga . Allah Taala jitni der tak chaahega mujhey sajde mein rehney dega. phir kaha jaeyga ke apna sar utha lo, maango diya jaeyga, kaho suna jaeyga, shafaat karo, shafaat qabool ki jaeygi. main apne rab ki us waqt aisi hamd bayan karunga ke jo Allah Taala mujhey sikhaaeyga. phir shafaat karunga aur mere liye had muqarrar kar di jaeygi aur main logon ko jahannam se nikal kar jannat mein dakhil kar doonga aur isi tarah sajde mein gir jaunga, teesri ya chothi martaba jahannam mein sirf wahi log baqi reh jaeinge jinhein Quran ne rokaa hai (yani jinke jahannam mein hamesha rehney ka zikr Quran mein sarahat ke sath hai) Qatada (Rahmatullahi-alaih) is mauqe par kaha kartey ke is se wo log murad hain jin par jahannam mein hamesha rehna wajib ho gaya hai."
6566,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''eik jamat jahannam se Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki shafaat ki wjah se nikley gii aur jannat mein dakhil hogi jinko ( jahannamii) ke naam se pukara jaaeyga.''
6567,"Haarisa-bin-Suraaqa bin-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin. Harisa badr ki ladai mein aik naa-maaloom teer lag janey ki wjah se Shahid ho gaey they aur unhon-ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! aapko malum hai ke Harisa se mujhey kitni mohabbat thi, agar wo jannat mein hai to is par main nahiin ro'ongii, warna aap dekhengey ke main kya karti hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke bewaqoof ho gaee ho, kya koi jannat aik hi hai, jannatein to bahut si hain aur Harisa ''firdause-aa'laa'' ( jannat ke oonchey darjey ( mein hai."
6568,"Allah ke rastey mein jihad ke liye aik subah ya aik Sham safar karna duniya aur jo kuchh usmein hai, se badh kar hai aur jannat mein tumhari aik kamaan ke barabar jagah ya aik qadam ke faasley ke barabar jagah duniya aur jo kuchh usmein hai, se behtar hai aur agar jannat ki aurton mein se koi aurat poori zameen ki taraf jhank kar dekh ley to aasman se lekar zameen tak munawwar kar de aur un tamam ko khushbu se bhar de aur uska dupatta ( duniya aur jo kuch usmein hai) se badh kar hai."
6569,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jannat mein jo bhi dakhil hoga usey uska jahannam ka thikana bhi dikhaya jaeyga ke agar nafarmani ki hoti (to wahan usey jagah miltii (taake wo aur zyada shukr karey aur jo bhi jahannam mein dakhil hoga usey uska jannat ka thikana bhi dikhaya jaeyga ke agar achchhey amal kiye hotey (to wahan jagah miltii) taake uske liye hasarat w afsos ka baais ho.
6570,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya : ya Rasulullah! qiyamat ke din aap ki shafaat ki khush-naseebi sabse zyada kon hasil karega? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey abu-Huraira! mera bhi khayal tha ke ye hadis tum se pahley aur koi mujh se nahi poochhega, kyonke hadis ke leney ke liye mein tumhari bahut zyada hirs dekha karta hun. qiyamat ke din meri shafaat ki khush-naseebi sabse zyada usey hasil hogi jisne kalima ( لا إله إلا الله ( Khuloos dil se kahaa."
6571,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main khub janta hun ke ahaley jahannam mein se kon sabse aakhir mein wahan se niklega aur ahle-jannat mein kon sabse aakhir mein usmein dakhil hoga. aik shakhs jahannam se ghutnon ke bal ghisattey huey niklega aur Allah Taala us se kahega ke jao aur jannat mein dakhil ho jao, wo jannat ke paas aayega lekin usey aisa malum hoga ke jannat bhari hui hai. chunanche wo wapas aayega aur arz karega : aey mere rab! maine jannat ko bharaa hua paya , Allah Taala phir us se kahega ke jao aur jannat mein dakhil ho jao. wo phir aayega lekin usey aisa malum hoga ke jannat bhari hui hai wo wapas lautey ga aur arz karega ke aey mere rab! maine jannat ko bharaa hua paya. Allah Taala farmaeyga jao aur jannat mein dakhil ho jao tumhen duniya aur us se dus guna diya jata hai ya (Allah taala farmaeyga ke) tumhen duniya ke dus guna diya jata hai. wo shakhs kahega to mera mazaaq banata hai halanke to shehanshaah hai. maine dekha ke is baat par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans diye aur aap ke aagey ke dandaaney Mubarak zahir ho gaey aur kaha jata hai ke wo jannat ka sabse kam darjey wala shakhs hoga."
6572,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : kya aap ne abu-Taalib ko koi nafa pahunchaya ?
6573,"kuchh logon ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya qiyamat ke din ham apne rab ko dekh sakengey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya suraj ko dekhney main tumhen koi dushwari hoti hai jabke is par koi badal (abr) wghaira na ho? sahaba ne arz kya : nahi ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya jab koi badal na ho to tumhen chaudahween raat ke chaand ko dekhney mein koi dushwari hoti hai? sahaba ne arz kya : nahi ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tum Allah Taala ko isi tarah qiyamat ke din dekhogey. Allah Taala logon ko jama karega aur kahega ke tum mein se jo shakhs jis cheez ki poojaa-paat kya karta tha wo usi ke peechhey lag jaey. chunanche jo log suraj ki parastish kya kartey they wo uske peechhey lag jaeinge aur jo log chaand ki puja kartey they wo uske peechhey ho lengey. jo log buton ki parastish kartey they wo unke peechhey lag jaeinge aur aakhir mein ye ummat baqi reh jaeygi aur is mein munaafeqeen ki jamat bhi hogi, us waqt Allah Taala unke samney is sura mein aayega jis ko wo pehchantey na hongey aur kahega ke main tumhara rab hun. log kahengey tujh se Allah ki panaah. ham apni jagah par us waqt tak raheingey jab tak ke hamara parwardigar hamarey samney na aaey. jab hamara rab hamarey paas aayega to ham usey pehchan lengey (kyonke wo hashr mein aik baar usko pahley dekh chukey hongey) phir haq taala is sura mein aayega jis ko wo pehchantey hongey aur unse kaha jaeyga (aao mere sath ho lo) main tumhara rab hun ! log kahengey ke to hamara rab hai, phir usi ke peechhey ho jaeinge aur jahannam par pul bana diya jaeyga Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main sabse pahlaa shakhs hunga jo us pul ko paar karunga aur us din rasulon ki dua ye hogi ke aey Allah ! mujh ko salamat rakhiyo . aey Allah ! mujh ko salamat rakhiyo aur wahan Sadan ke kaanton ki tarah aankdey hongey. tum ne Sadan ke kaantey dekhey hain? sahaba kiram ne arz kya ji haan dekhey hain ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo phir Sadan ke kaanton ki tarah hongey albatta uski lambai chaudai Allah ke siwa aur koi nahi janta. wo logon ko unke aamaal ke mutabiq uchak lengey aur is tarah unmein se kuchh to apne aa'mal ki wjah se halaak ho jaeinge aur kuchh ka aa'mal raai ke daney ke barabar hoga, phir wo nijat pa jaeyga aakhir jab Allah Taala apne bandon ke darmyan faisley se farigh ho jaeyga aur jahannam se unhein nikaalnaa chaahega jinhein nikalney ki uski marzi hogi. yani wo jinhoney kalima (لا إله إلا الله) ki gawahi di hogi aur Allah Taala farishton ko hukm dega ke wo aisey logon ko jahannam se nikaaley. Farishtey unhein sajdon ke nishanat se pehchan lengey kyonke Allah Taala ne aag par haram kar diya hai ke wo ibne-Aadam ke jism mein sajdon ke nishan ko khaaey . chunanche Farishtey un logon ko nikaley gey . ye jal kar koiley ho chukey hongey phir un par pani chhidkaa jaeyga jisey (ماء الحياة) zindagi bakhshney wala pani kehtey hain. us waqt wo is tarah taro-taazaa ho jaeinge jaisey sailaab ke baad zarkhaiz (زرخیز) zameen mein daana ug aata hai. aik aisa shakhs baqi reh jaeyga jiska chehra jahannam ki taraf hoga aur wo kahega aey mere rab! uski badboo ne mujhey pareshan kar diya hai aur uski lipat ne mujhey jhulsaa diya hai aur uski tezi ne mujhey jalaa daala hai, zara mera munh aag ki taraf se dusri taraf pher de. wo isi tarah Allah se dua karta rahega. aakhir Allah Taala farmaeyga agar main tera ye mutalba pura kar dun to kahin to koi dusri cheez maangnii shuru na kar de. wo shakhs arz karega nahi, teri izzat ki qism ! main iske siwa koi dusri cheez nahi maangon ga . chunanche iska chehra jahannam ki taraf se dusri taraf pher diya jaeyga ab iske baad wo kahega . aey mere rab! mujhey jannat ke darwazey ke qareeb kar dijiye. Allah Taala farmaeyga kya tu ney abhi yaqin nahi dilaya tha ke iske siwa aur koi cheez nahi maangey ga. afsos ! aey ibne-Aadam ! to bahut zyada wada khilaf hai. phir wo barabar isi tarah dua karta rahega to Allah Taala farmaeyga ke agar main teri ye dua qabool kar loon to to phir iske ilawa kuchh aur cheez maangney lagey ga. wo shakhs kahega nahi, teri izzat ki qism ! main iske siwa aur koi cheez tujh se nahi maangon ga aur wo Allah se ahad w paiman karega ke iske siwa ab koi aur cheez nahi maangey ga. chunanche Allah Taala usey jannat ke darwazey ke qareeb kar dega. jab wo jannat ke andar ki ne'maton ko dekhega to jitni der tak Allah Taala chaahega wo shakhs khamosh rahega, phir kahega aey mere rab ! mujhey jannat mein dakhil kar de. Allah Taala farmaeyga ke kya tu ney ye yaqin nahi dilaya tha ke ab to iske siwa koi cheez nahi maangey ga. aey ibne-Aadam ! afsos, to kitna wada khilaf hai. wo shakhs arz karega aey mere rab! mujhey apni makhlooq ka sabse bad-bakht banda na banaa. wo barabar dua karta rahega yahan tak ke Allah Taala hans dega. jab Allah hans dega to us shakhs ko jannat mein dakhil honey ki ijazat mil jaeygi. jab wo andar chala jaeyga to us se kaha jaeyga ke falan cheez ki khahish kar chunanche wo uski khahish karega. phir us se kaha jaeyga ke falan cheez ki khahish karo, chunanche wo phir khahish karega yahan tak ke uski khuwaahishaat khatm ho jaeyngi to Allah Taala ki taraf se kaha jaeyga ke teri ye saari khuwaahishaat poori ki jati hain aur itni hi zyada ne'matein aur di jati hain. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi sanad se kaha ke ye shakhs jannat mein sabse aakhir mein dakhil honey wala hoga."
6574,"Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bhi us waqt Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath baithey huey they aur unhon-ne unki kisi baat par aetraz nahi kya lekin jab Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hadis ke us tukdey tak pahunchey ke tumhari ye saari khuwaahishaat poori ki jati hain aur itni hi aur zyada ne'matein di jati hain to Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhari ye saari khuwaahishaat poori ki jati hain aur us se dus guna aur zyada ne'matein di jati hain. aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke nahi maine yun hi suna hai, ye sab cheezein aur itni hi aur."
6575,aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ke main tum se pahley hi hauz par maujood rahoonga.
6576,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main apne hauz par tum se pahley hi maujood rahunga aur tum mein se kuchh log mere samney laey jaeinge phir unhein mere samney se hata diya jaeyga to main kahunga ke aey mere rab! ye mere sathi hain lekin mujh se kaha jaeyga ke aap nahi jantey ke unhon-ne aap ke baad Deen mein kya-kyaa nai cheezein eiijaad kar li thin. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Aasim ne abu-Wayeil se ki, unse Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan farmaayaa."
6577,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tumhaarey samney hi mera hauz hoga wo itna bada hai jitna (mulk Sham ke do gaanv) jarbaa aur azroohaa ke darmyan fasla hai.''
6578,kausar se murad bahut zyada bhalai (khair kaseer) hai jo Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di hai. abu-Bashar ne bayan kya ke maine Saeed-bin-Jubair se kaha ke kuchh logon ka khayal hai ke kausar jannat mein aik nehar hai to unhon-ne kaha ke jo nehar jannat mein hai wo bhi us khair (bhalaaii) ka aik hissa hai jo Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di hai.
6579,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meraa hauz aik mahiney ki doori ke barabar hoga. uska pani doodh se zyada safaid aur uski khushbu mushk se zyada achi hogi aur uske koozey (gharey) aasmaan ke sitaron ki tadaad ke barabar hongey. jo shakhs usmein se aik martaba pi lega wo phir kabhi bhi (maidaan mahshar mein) piyaasaa na hoga.''
6580,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere hauz ki lambai itni hogi jitni iila aur Yaman aur Shahar san'aa ke darmyan ki lambai hai. aur wahan itni badi tadaad mein pyaley hongey jitney aasman ke sitaron ki tadaad hai.''
6581,aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan kya ke main jannat mein chal raha tha ke main aik nehar par pahuncha iske donon kinaron par khauldaar motiyon ke gunbad baney huey they. maine puchha : Jibraeel ! ye kya hai? unhon-ne kaha ye kausar hai jo aap ke rab ne aapko diya hai. maine dekha ke uski khushbu ya mitti tez mushk jaisi thi. rawi ko shak tha.
6582,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere kuchh sathi hauz par mere samney laey jaeinge aur main unhein pehchan loonga lekin phir wo mere samney se hata diye jaengey. main is par kahunga ke ye to mere sathi hain. lekin mujh se kaha jaeyga ke aapko malum nahi ke unhon-ne aap ke baad kya-kyaa nai cheezein eiijaad kar li thiin.''
6583,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main apne hauz kausar par tum se pahley maujood rahoonga. jo shakhs bhi meri taraf se guzrey ga wo iska pani piey ga aur jo iska pani piey ga wo phir kabhi piyaasaa nahi hoga aur wahan kuchh aisey log bhi aaeingey jinhein main pahchaanoon ga aur wo mujhey pahchaanein gey lekin phir unhein mere samney se hata diya jaaeyga.''
6584,mein gawahi deta hun ke maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis isi tarah suni thi aur wo us hadis mein kuchh zyadti ke sath bayan kartey they. (yani ye ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaaengey ke) main kahunga ke ye to mujh mein se hain) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha jaeyga ke aapko nahi malum ke unhon-ne aap ke baad Deen mein kya- kya nai cheezein eiijaad kar li thin. is par main kahunga ke door hon wo shakhs jisne mere baad Deen mein tabdili kar li thii.
6585,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din mere sahaba mein se aik jamat mujh par pesh ki jaeygi. phir wo hauz se door kar diye jaengey. mein arz karunga : aey mere rab! ye to mere sahaba hain. Allah Taala farmaeyga ke tumhen malum nahi ke unhon-ne tumharey baad kya-kyaa nai cheezein ghad li thin ? ye log (deen se) ultey paanw wapas lot gaey they.'' (doosri sanad) Shuaib-bin-abii-Hamza ne bayan kya, unse Zohri ne ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se (فيجلون) (bajaaey (فيحلؤون)) ke bayan kartey they. aur Aqeel (فيحلؤون) bayan kartey they aur Zubaidi ne bayan kya, unse Zohri ne, unse Muhammad-bin Ali ne, unse Ubaidullah bin abi Raafe ne, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
6586,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' hauz par mere sahaba ki aik jamat aaeygii . phir unhein us se door kar diya jaeyga mein arz karunga mere rab! ye to mere sahaba hain. Allah Taala farmaeyga ke tumhen malum nahi ke unhon-ne tumharey baad kya-kyaa nai cheezein eiijaad kar li thin, ye ultey paon (Islam se) wapas lot gaey they.''"
6587,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa  ''main (hauz par) khada hunga ke aik jamat mere samney aaeygii aur jab main unhein pehchan loonga to aik shakhs (farishta) mere aur unke darmyan se niklega aur unse kahega ke idhar aao . main kahunga ke kidhar ? wo kahega ke Allah ki qism jahannam ki taraf. main kahunga ke unke halaat kya hain? wo kahega ke ye log aap ke baad ultey paon (deen se) wapas lot gaey they. phir aik aur giroh mere samney aayega aur jab main unhein bhi pehchan loonga to aik shakhs (farishta) mere aur unke darmyan mein se niklega aur unse kahega ke idhar aao . main poochhoon ga ke kahaan? to wo kahega, Allah ki qism ! jahannam ki taraf. main kahunga ke unke halaat kya hain? farishta kahega ke ye log aap ke baad ultey paon wapas lot gaey they. main samajhta hun ke un girohon mein se aik aadmi bhi nahi bachchey ga. un sab ko dozakh mein ley jaengey."
6588,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere ghar aur mere member ke darmyan ki jagah ka jannat ke baaghon mein se aik baagh hai aur mera member mere hauz par hai.
6589,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main hauz par tum se pahley maujood hunga ."
6590,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur shohdaa Uhud ke liye is tarah dua ki jis tarah maiyat ke liye janazey mein dua ki jati hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif laey aur farmaya logo ! main tum se aagey jaaunga aur tum par gawah rahunga aur main Allah ki qism apne hauz ki taraf us waqt bhi dekh raha hun aur mujhey zameen ke khazaanon ki kunjiyaan di gaee hain ya farmaya ke zameen ki kunjiyaan di gaee hain. Allah ki qism ! main tumharey barey mein is baat se nahi darta ke tum mere baad shirk karogey, albatta us se darta hun ke tum duniya ke laalach mein pad kar aik doosrey se hasad karne lago gey ."
6591,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hauz ka zikr kya aur farmaya ke (wo itna bada hai) jitni Madina aur san'aa ke darmyan doori hai."
6592,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye irshad suna, usmein itna zyada hai ke aap ka hauz itna lamba hoga jitni san'aa aur Madina ke darmyan doori hai. is par mustaurid ne kaha : kya aap ne bartanon wali riwayat nahi sunii? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. mustaurid ne kaha ke ke usmein bartan (peeney ke) is tarah nazar aaeingey jis tarah aasman mein sitaarey nazar aatey hain."
6593,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main hauz par maujood rahunga aur dekhunga ke tum mein se kon mere paas aata hai. phir kuchh logon ko mujh se alag kar diya jaeyga mein arz karunga ke aey mere rab! ye to mere hi aadmi hain aur meri ummat ke log hain. mujh se kaha jaeyga ke tumhen malum bhi hai unhon-ne tumharey baad kya kaam kiye they? Allah ki qism ye musalsal ultey paon laut'tey rahe. (deen Islam se phir gaey) ibne-abi-Mulaika (jo ke ye hadis Asma se riwayat farmatey hain) kaha kartey they ke aey Allah ! ham is baat se teri panah maangtey hain ke ham ultey paon (deen se) lot jayen ya apne Deen ke barey mein fitna mein daal diye jaaein. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke sura mominoon mein jo Allah Taala ka farman hai) أعقابكم تنكصو‏) iska mana bhi yahi hai ke tum Deen se apni eidiyon ke bal ultey phir gaey they yani Islam se murtad ho gaey they.
